# CORS - Allowed Origins (comma-separated list of URLs that can access the API)
# Default: http://localhost:9080 (local development)
# To allow additional IP addresses or domains, add them comma-separated:
# Example: http://localhost:9080,http://192.168.1.100:9080,http://10.0.0.50:9080
# For all local network: http://localhost:9080,http://127.0.0.1:9080
