# Allowed IPs - Additional IP addresses allowed to access the API (comma-separated)
# These IPs can access the API regardless of CORS origin
# Default: 127.0.0.1 (localhost only)
# Example: 127.0.0.1,192.168.1.0/24,10.0.0.50
